Along with [[Windows_95|m.086n_]] 's release , [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] debuted [[MSN|m.0198jf]] Dial-up , a subscription-based dial-up online service that it later turned into an [[Internet_service_provider|m.0pjxv]] named [[MSN|m.0198jf]] Dial-up .
The current website and suite of [[Mobile_app|m.0h94y36]] offered by [[MSN|m.0198jf]] was first introduced by [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] in 2014 as part of a complete redesign and relaunch .
[[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] 's original news website , msnbc.com  , which launched in 1996 , was also tied closely to the [[Internet|m.03rlt]] Start portal.

In 1998 , the largely underutilized MSN.com domain name was combined with [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] [[Internet|m.03rlt]] Start and reinvented as both a web portal and as the brand for a family of sites produced inside [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] 's Interactive Media Group .
[[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] said it would be more app-like due to the speed of [[Internet_Explorer_10|m.0gk_qly]] .
This move was part of [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] 's strategy to improve its online offerings using the [[Microsoft_Windows|m.04r_8]] brand name .

The group of [[Windows_Live|m.08nvnv]] services used [[Web_2.0|m.05b058]] technology to offer features and functionality through a web browser that were traditionally only available through dedicated software programs .
Following the launch of [[Windows_Live|m.08nvnv]] , the [[MSN|m.0198jf]] brand took on a different focus .

In 2012 , [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] began to phase out the [[Windows_Live|m.08nvnv]] brand , referring to each service separately by its individual brand name without any [[Windows_8|m.0gvswcc]] prefix or association .
The new [[MSN|m.0198jf]] portal features a new version of the logo that follows a style similar to other current [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] products .
Signing into [[MSN|m.0198jf]] with a [[Microsoft_account|m.068tcp]] allows for personalized content to appear and to be synchronized across devices on the website and in the [[MSN|m.0198jf]] .

The redesign of the website led to the closure of [[MSN|m.0198jf]] 's longtime personalized home page service My [[MSN|m.0198jf]] ' , which was made up of customized [[RSS_feeds|m.0n5tx]] , as the new website no longer supports user-specified RSS content .
With the 2014 relaunch , [[MSN|m.0198jf]] now supports responsive design and eliminates the need for a separate mobile website .
Current suite of [[Mobile_app|m.0h94y36]] .

After its acquisition of [[Microsoft_Mobile|m.010f8k1s]] , [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] also started bundling [[MSN|m.0198jf]] services with its [[Series_30+|m.012m5w0z]] , though currently the only supported model is the [[Nokia_215|m.012m5sw7]] .
In addition to these [[Mobile_app|m.0h94y36]] , [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] develops a [[MSN_China|m.09k4r7l]] specifically for [[MSN_China|m.09k4r7l]] .

The [[MSN|m.0198jf]] Weather app  shows weather from a user 's current location or any other location worldwide , and it allows users to define their favorite places , which will synchronize back to the web portal and across devices .
It also powers various predictive features within [[Microsoft|m.04sv4]] 's [[Microsoft_Cortana|m.0_x5sss]] virtual assistant .

[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] Dorie [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]]  was a Messmen Third Class .
the [[United_States_Navy|m.07wg3]] noted for his bravery during the attack on Pearl Harbor on December 7 , 1941 .
The [[Navy_Cross|m.02d1w_]] now precedes the [[Navy_Distinguished_Service_Medal|m.039sxx]] .

[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] 's acts were heavily publicized in the black press , making him the iconic emblem of the war for blacks -- their Number One Hero -- thereby energizing black support for the war effort against a colored Japanese enemy .
Nearly two years after Pearl Harbor , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was killed in action when was sunk by a Japanese submarine during the [[Battle_of_Makin|m.04f2l7]] .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was a good student and was a fullback on the football team at Waco ? s A.J. Moore High School .
On January 25 , 1937 , at age 17 , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] began attending the eighth grade again .
Forced to repeat the grade the following year , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] decided to drop out of school .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] filled his time squirrel hunting with a .22 rifle and completed a correspondence course in taxidermy .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] applied to join the [[Civilian_Conservation_Corps|m.0260s]] , but was not accepted .
At that time [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was tall and weighed more than .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] worked on his father ? s farm until shortly before his 20th birthday .

Following training at the [[Naval_Station_Norfolk|m.03mqqw]] , Virginia , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was assigned to the ammunition ship , but on January 2 , 1940 , was transferred to the battleship , where [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] became the main cook .
In July , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was on temporary duty on the at the Secondary Battery Gunnery School .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] returned to his ship in August and was promoted to Ship 's Cook , Third Class .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] 's nickname Dorie apparently originated in a typographical error .

After [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was nominated for recognition for his actions on December 7 , 1941 , the [[Pittsburgh_Courier|m.0722y3]] released a story on March 14 , 1942 , that gave his name as Dorie [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] .
On December 7 , 1941 , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] awoke at 0600 .

After serving breakfast mess , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was collecting laundry when the first of nine torpedoes to hit the West Virginia was launched at 0757 by Lieutenant Commander Shigeharu Murata of the Japanese carrier [[Japanese_aircraft_carrier_Akagi|m.019tb_]] .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] headed for his battle station , an [[Anti-aircraft_warfare|m.012pyc]] battery magazine amidship , only to discover that torpedo damage had destroyed it .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] went instead to Times Square , a central spot where the fore to aft and port to starboard passageways crossed , and reported himself available for other duty .

[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was spotted by Lieutenant Commander Doir C. Johnson , the ship 's communications officer , who ordered the powerfully built sailor to accompany him to the bridge to assist with moving the ship 's captain , [[Mervyn_Bennion|m.08xm2m]] , who had a gaping wound in his abdomen where [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] had apparently been hit by shrapnel .

[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] and another sailor lifted the skipper and , unable to remove him from the bridge , carried him from an exposed position on the damaged bridge to a sheltered spot behind the conning tower .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was not familiar with the machine gun , but White and Delano told him what to do .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] had served both men as a room steward and knew them well .
White had loaded ammunition into both guns and assigned [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] the starboard gun .
[[Mervyn_Bennion|m.08xm2m]] was only partially conscious at this point , and died soon after .

When the attack finally lessened , White ordered [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] to help move injured sailors through oil and water to the quarterdeck , thereby unquestionably saving the lives of a number of people who might otherwise have been lost .

With the ship heavily damaged by the bombs , torpedoes and following explosions , the crew prevented her from capsizing by counter-flooding a number of compartments , and the West Virginia sank to the harbor bottom as her crew -- including [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] -- abandoned ship .
On December 15 , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was transferred to the .

The [[National_Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Colored_People|m.05hpy]] asked President [[Franklin_D._Roosevelt|m.02yy8]] to award the [[Distinguished_Service_Cross_(United_States)|m.02fwk3]] to the unknown Negro sailor .
On March 12 , 1942 , Dr. [[Lawrence_D._Reddick|m.04jkppq]] announced , after corresponding with the Navy , that the name of the unknown Negro sailor was [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] .

The next day , Senator [[James_Forrestal|m.01gft0]] M. Mead  introduced a Senate Bill  to award [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] the [[Medal_of_Honor|m.015cl6]] , although [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] did not yet know the basis for [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] 's deeds .
Four days later , Representative [[John_D._Dingell,_Sr.|m.04cl18]] D. Dingell , Sr.  introduced a matching bill  .
On March 21 , The African-American newspaper [[Pittsburgh_Courier|m.0722y3]] initiated a write-in campaign to send [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] to the Naval Academy .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was recognized as one of the first US heroes of World War II .
Negro organizations began a campaign to give [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] additional recognition .
The [[Southern_Negro_Youth_Congress|m.026yhyl]] launched a signature campaign on April 17 -- 19 .
On May 10 , the [[National_Negro_Congress|m.026yjbn]] denounced [[Frank_Knox|m.02jgz6]] 's recommendation against awarding [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] the [[Medal_of_Honor|m.015cl6]] .
On May 11 , President [[Franklin_D._Roosevelt|m.02yy8]] approved the [[Navy_Cross|m.02d1w_]] for [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] .
On May 27 , 1942 , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was personally recognized by Admiral [[Chester_W._Nimitz|m.0f61h]] , Commander in Chief , Pacific Fleet , aboard the aircraft carrier .
[[Chester_W._Nimitz|m.0f61h]] presented [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] with the [[Navy_Cross|m.02d1w_]] , at the time the third-highest Navy award for gallantry during combat .

[[Chester_W._Nimitz|m.0f61h]] said of [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] 's commendation , This marks the first time in this conflict that such high tribute has been made in the Pacific Fleet to a member of his race and I 'm sure that the future will see others similarly honored for brave acts .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was promoted to Mess Attendant First Class on June 1 , 1942 .
On June , 27 , The [[Pittsburgh_Courier|m.0722y3]] called for [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] to be allowed to return home for a war bond tour like white heroes .
On November 23 , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] returned to Pearl Harbor and was ordered on a war bond tour while still attached to the heavy cruiser .
In its February 6 , 1943 issue , the [[Pittsburgh_Courier|m.0722y3]] continued to hammer to return [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] for a war bond tour .

The caption to [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] ? s photo in the article read , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] fought ... Keeps Mop , while another hero of the Pearl Harbor attack received an officer 's commission .
It said that [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was too important waiting tables in the Pacific to return him , even though in fact [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was already on tour .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] reported for duty at [[Puget_Sound_Navy_Yard|m.068rt]] on May 15 , 1943 .
[[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was made a Petty Officer , Ship ? s Cook Third Class , on June 1 when [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] reported to the escort carrier .
After training in Hawaii , the [[USS_Liscome_Bay_(CVE-56)|m.026hhj]] took part in the [[Makin_(islands)|m.03d4mj7]] beginning November 20 , 1943 .
There were 272 survivors from the crew of over 900 , but [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was not among them .
Along with two-thirds of the crew , [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was listed as presumed dead .
On December 7 , 1943 -- two years after [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] 's heroic actions at Pearl Harbor -- his parents were informed that their son was missing in action .
A memorial service was held on April 30 , 1944 , at the [[Waco,_Texas|m.0106dv]] , Second Baptist Church , sponsored by the Victory Club .
On May 28 , a granite marker was dedicated at Moore High School to honor [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] .
On November 25 , Secretary of the Navy [[James_Forrestal|m.01gft0]] announced to the public that [[Doris_Miller|m.0198hp]] was presumed dead .
[[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] also known as [[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] ,  is a Venezuelan actress .

[[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] began acting in [[Telenovelas|m.0n5qw]] in 1986 when [[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] participated in Cristal and the miniseries Mansion de Luxe alongside another famous Venezuelan actor , Carlos Mata .

[[Señora_(telenovela)|m.0fkbfw]] became an instant hit all over [[Venezuela|m.07ylj]] and other Latin American countries for producer Radio Caracas Television/RCTV , and [[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] became a super-star immediately .
In Amanda Sabater , [[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] played the title character alongside [[Flavio_Caballero|m.0b1j9h]] and Gabriel Márquez among others .
Another great success was El Desprecio  , a soap opera that was unique in not depicting a happy ending and being loosely based on [[Robert_Graves|m.09svs]] ' [[Claudius_the_God|m.016bnz]] .
In addition to working in Venezuelan and Peruvian productions [[Maricarmen_Regueiro|m.0198rw]] has also worked in [[Argentina|m.0jgd]] .
The character also appears in [[Buffy_the_Vampire_Slayer_Season_Eight|m.0284r17]] , the canonical continuation of the series .
[[Andrew_Wells|m.0198sn]] is the younger brother of Tucker Wells , who summoned hellhounds to attack the Prom in the Season Three episode [[The_Prom_(Buffy_the_Vampire_Slayer)|m.073f6y]] .
